---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="About Simple Calculators"
  description="Learn who runs Simple Calculators, why we build calculator tools, and how we maintain quality, usability, and transparent assumptions."
>
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">About Simple Calculators</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-600">
        Simple Calculators is an independent project focused on practical, easy-to-use calculator tools for everyday
        financial, health, and conversion questions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Our mission</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
        We build calculators that are fast, mobile-friendly, and understandable. Each tool is designed to show clear
        inputs and outputs without unnecessary complexity.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
        Our goal is to help people make better first-pass estimates before they speak with a licensed professional.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">How we maintain quality</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
        <li>We publish formula assumptions and limitations on key calculator pages.</li>
        <li>We review edge cases where estimates can become misleading.</li>
        <li>We update pages when formulas, guidance, or usability issues are identified.</li>
        <li>We keep tools free and accessible without requiring an account.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Important disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
        Calculator outputs are estimates and educational guidance only. They are not legal, tax, financial, medical,
        or investment advice.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
        For decisions involving money, health, or legal obligations, confirm details with a qualified professional.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
        Questions, corrections, or suggestions are welcome at
        <a href="mailto:hello@simplecalculators.io" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 underline ml-1">hello@simplecalculators.io</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
